                     <interp inst="t18250915-322-person1619" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I took the prisoner into custody. He said he would take me where the spoon was.</p>
               <p>
                  <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="182509150120"></xptr>Prisoner. I did confess to the Lord Mayor that I took the spoon.</p>
